description:
KP Youth Employment program is all about Freelancing. To empower the youth of KP (Pakistan) to start freelancing and work on different projects from their home.

Students will learn how to 

Make accounts on different online marketplaces such as upwork, freelancer & peopleperhour etc.

How to bid on different projects

How to Write a cover letter

How to communicate with client

Payment Methods such as Skrill, Payoneer & Bank Transfer
title: KP Youth Employment Program
